installationInstructions.author: Robert from Lake Zurich, IL
installationInstructions.title: Appliance Color Change To Match New Countertops
installationInstructions.content: Removed 6-8 screws on inside of door.  Front cover came off, painted it black.  Removed 6 screws holding escutcheon to door assembly.  Swapped out white one for black.  Reassembled door and was done.  Dishwaser was in great shape and replacing escutcheon and knob was under 50. 00 Delivered.  Compared to 500. 00 For a new one and  my wife was real happy!! Thanks
